headline: Is Analyst Uncertainty and Insider Buying Shifting the Long-Term Narrative for Intuitive Surgical (ISRG)?
summary: In recent days, Intuitive Surgical has drawn investor attention following a series of analyst recommendation changes, downward earnings estimate revisions, and news of a significant stock purchase by Senator Markwayne Mullin in late September 2025. While the company remains a leader in the global robotic surgery market, a contrast between optimistic brokerage ratings and more cautious analyst revisions has introduced fresh uncertainty ahead of its anticipated earnings release.
